description: OPEN HOUSE 3/22 11-12pm CLOSING CREDIT UP TO $10K.  Built in 2021, 69 Preble #3 is a modern 2 Bed/2.5 bath with PRIVATE roof deck, DEEDED garage parking and 1,460 sq ft living area. Property features an open-concept design with hardwood floors + recessed lighting throughout. 9 ft+ ceilings + oversized windows. Contemporary kitchen with Quartz island, equipped with Fisher/Paykel stainless appliances, ideal for quick meals or dinner parties! Living area has gas fireplace. Large Primary Bedroom with en suite bath, double vanity + oversized tile shower with frameless glass enclosure. In-unit laundry + Central AC! Heated garage parking, easy access to public transit, major highways and South Boston beaches provide the ultimate convenience for city living. PRIVATE roof deck has outdoor seating/dining, breathtaking views and an outdoor gas fireplace, perfect for relaxing or hosting guests. Experience the best of comfort, style, and location all in one!
